{"tid":1388580,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"[和理非回合]連儂放映會 遍地問花 走入社區 全民參與 打破同溫層","createTime":"2019-07-30T17:29:09.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-02T11:16:17.000Z","uid":114654,"like":36,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":20,"replies":[{"pid":"f9ba1b2dc63ab342eb4f71e2de4c08010d66a6d4","tid":1388580,"uid":114654,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-30T17:29:09.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/h0N9zcQ.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fh0N9zcQ.jpg&h=7a3f82f7&s={SIZE}\" /> <br />\n我地係一群港島東區長大生活既和理非<br />\n見到近期運動開始遇到樽頸，政府繼續龜縮做錄音機，黑警用既暴力不斷升級，<br />\n我地只可以硬食催淚彈同警棍，每次行動完左都有幾十個義士被捕。<br />\n但社區入面好多大家口中既廢老廢中，由於受紅媒洗腦新聞影響，不斷指責我地既同路人。<br />\n於是我地膽粗粗自己籌旗班物資同設備，想係社區入面播Ｄ紅媒永遠唔會播既片段，比街坊睇睇真相而唔係假新聞。<br />\n<br />\n其實我地既裝備都係好土炮式：簡單一部手提投影機、一塊投影幕、一個揚聲器、手提發電機同兩張櫈<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/Uy5nUo6.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FUy5nUo6.jpg&h=da1ac2ed&s={SIZE}\" /> <br />\n我地係星期日同星期二係西灣河既運儂牆舉辦左兩晚，時間由夜晚7點至11點左右短短幾個鐘頭，反應都比我地預期中好<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/ZwhaiVN.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FZwhaiVN.jpg&h=c8ac4b95&s={SIZE}\" /> <br />\n唔單止圍觀既人多，收到大量街坊既關心支持，佢地拎左好多水、食物同其他物資(BTW:但因為我地和理非場合都用唔著咁多　會安排拎返上前線<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />)<br />\n更加有街坊想金錢上支援出一分力，完全係我地意料之外未諗過點處理，所以婉拒左，我地都研究緊有咩方法形式可以集合大家既力量幫到有需要既人。<br />\n但最最重要既係聽到好多中老年既街坊FEEDBACK，話點解TVB睇唔到呢D片既，原來政府/黑警係咁仆街既，更加有興趣睇隔離連儂牆上面大家既心聲同文宣，<br />\n仲有好多家庭入面唯一／少數既同路人，平時屋企冇條件同家人討論如果一講就炒大鑊，好需要呢種場合去同其他同路人交流發表意見。<br />\n<br />\n我地黎緊都會KEEP住係港島東區舉辦希望同更多街坊宣傳，暫定星期四晚會係筲箕灣巴士總站再搞。<br />\n<strong><span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">但我地志不在此，最希望可以全港各區都有手足一齊做，做到遍地開花全港參與</span></span></strong><br />\n收到風知道其他區都有搞緊類似既放映會，<br />\n如果有手足做緊/有志參與既可以一齊組織人手宣傳、交流經驗心得，共享物資設備。<br />\n請大家加入我地TG GROUP：<a href=\"http://bit.ly/18districts\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fbit.ly%2F18districts&d=JyEZwpqAG2Vgd3IXgRp6kbhWJNg3BDkm8i4jVfgHOzw%3D&h=7ebf096d\" target=\"_blank\">http://bit.ly/18districts</a>"},{"pid":"4f482553d81f2903c082efafcfef1abdb46a81e1","tid":1388580,"uid":114654,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-30T17:32:01.000Z","msg":"會唔會有啲咩法律問題?<br />\n<br />\nBy Law&rsquo;s Friend:<br />\n- 擺街放新聞應該要擺邊？<br />\n（Projector / Projecting Screen)<br />\nAnywhere that can allow reasonable passage of pedestrians after setting up<br />\n<br />\n- 使唔使申請?<br />\nLess than 30 ppl no need<br />\n<br />\n- 多過幾多人會變非法集會?<br />\nNot unlawful assembly if no action that make other people reasonably worry abt breach of peace. But could be unauthorised assembly if more than 30 ppl. <br />\n<br />\n- 遇到警察應該點處理？<br />\nIf the police wanna record ID number and name, they can <br />\nBut other than that, they shouldn&rsquo;t be able to do anything <br />\n<br />\n- 如到對家動手可以點?<br />\nThat&rsquo;s why it is better to have more ppl doing this together, and whenever there are quarrels, there should be ppl filming <br />\n<br />\n- 被檢控後可以點?<br />\nFind a lawyer once you get arrested, before the arrival of lawyer don&rsquo;t say anything to police apart from name and hkid no.It is not so soon that one is prosecuted"},{"pid":"e1ee90b7763f9907b70711f1b2ddee232dcc201c","tid":1388580,"uid":280593,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-30T17:33:27.000Z","msg":"去膠鐡站"},{"pid":"f489cb23701f37ee5d612abbf6e3d8b377673445","tid":1388580,"uid":294095,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-30T17:34:13.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"60f9da9abb20f747590f1b3b7047697220d4383c","tid":1388580,"uid":114654,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-30T17:37:21.000Z","msg":"岩岩星期二果晚因為網上做左好多宣傳，所以參與人數都比較多，同時對家都好多人黎搞事<br />\n<a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/1386892\" target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/1386892</a><br />\n短短幾個鐘頭已經至少有4批人黎嘈，甚至郁手，所以有足夠人手睇住個場都好重要<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b0985966dfd6f0725f67d9f607ca5dd287e991ba","tid":1388580,"uid":294095,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-30T17:42:54.000Z","msg":"推<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4fde370ed58456d7d6357f2567fae0f6c8184378","tid":1388580,"uid":114654,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-30T17:44:07.000Z","msg":"各有各做 爭取每一分支持<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"32a4f685d5e82deb2da6e9f040504a886df6b560","tid":1388580,"uid":61422,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-30T17:44:44.000Z","msg":"搞埋講壇/公民教育演講/辯論大會會唔會更好？廢老咁多意見但係好多基本概念都搞唔清<br />\n畀個機會佢地發表下再逐點指正番佢地，好過由得佢地日日喺屋企/街鳩up殘害他人精神。唔係嘅話到時就算真係成功有真普選，呢班民智未開嘅人都拎住好撚多票"},{"pid":"796415925b424c60e9efb194b88d59e67121ad1e","tid":1388580,"uid":294095,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-30T17:46:15.000Z","msg":"推<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4f4fb3789d7a8a20758df8d3e02884876ada1c89","tid":1388580,"uid":294095,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-30T17:49:35.000Z","msg":"推<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"06ba5875f99eb06caf0c14fad6fe8c48080823ee","tid":1388580,"uid":294095,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-30T17:52:55.000Z","msg":"推<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c14a343e7b63b94de2674ef350960f06044e5a34","tid":1388580,"uid":114654,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"32a4f685d5e82deb2da6e9f040504a886df6b560","tid":1388580,"uid":61422,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-30T17:44:44.000Z","msg":"搞埋講壇/公民教育演講/辯論大會會唔會更好？廢老咁多意見但係好多基本概念都搞唔清<br />\n畀個機會佢地發表下再逐點指正番佢地，好過由得佢地日日喺屋企/街鳩up殘害他人精神。唔係嘅話到時就算真係成功有真普選，呢班民智未開嘅人都拎住好撚多票"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-30T17:53:27.000Z","msg":"非大台 我地都摸緊咩形式最好 歡迎加入討論<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d3099a00a97bdaf93a593b43ae1830326fc6dbaa","tid":1388580,"uid":265019,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-30T17:53:37.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/eoAK8d9.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FeoAK8d9.png&h=b7586def&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/gFabOea.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FgFabOea.png&h=0210e024&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/ugcQ3Nv.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FugcQ3Nv.png&h=2c38784d&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"71c571ece456768650d7c88139d1a2dc4d76b771","tid":1388580,"uid":294095,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-30T17:56:15.000Z","msg":"推<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"574793fe128f0a38e65f425ff8df0eff81ed8a32","tid":1388580,"uid":114654,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-30T18:00:34.000Z","msg":"推<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"05906d714ac29e3ccee1a325612eefdcf790459c","tid":1388580,"uid":294095,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-30T18:05:09.000Z","msg":"推<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3855f29423390bdfad709045de7f27ecf891fbbe","tid":1388580,"uid":294095,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-30T18:08:26.000Z","msg":"推<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgm